{"tid":1605830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣組入】全球文宣應該針對中國在該國引起既負面影響來宣傳引起共鳴","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:03:44.000Z","uid":162866,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb5078b16392ba2217cc37f09cc2efd9bdf8b25","tid":1605830,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"你係外國登報一味話香港點點點根本好難引起對方共鳴，因為人地未必留意香港，可能睇完就算<br />\n<br />\n登報要針對中國對果一國引起既負面影響來宣傳<br />\n<br />\n例如對美國就用貿易戰，廉價貨搶美國人職位類<br />\n<br />\n日本韓國就用釣魚台主權問題類<br />\n<br />\n歐洲英國就用肛交所企圖收購倫交所控制經濟類<br />\n<br />\n務求引起全球仇中情緒<br />\n<br />\n來緊主要戰場就係公關戰<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好浪費錢登報淨係講香港點點點<br />\n<br />\n要show比國際睇中國點樣威脅緊該國國民既生活<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e816ca39d3a7ff0654c3dc00d9a4191915b23c38","tid":1605830,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"850508db1a55ba73bc01938346de12d32a9ffe13","tid":1605830,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"推！煲大中國威脅論外國人先會care<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968bea6e0260ed1363ff6de82937e26ad72f0ae1","tid":1605830,"uid":34235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"其實大把嘢講可以引起他國嘅共鳴<br />\n之前去英國，當地人係咁屌鳩班大陸人炒樓，暴買，搶學位同職位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4ad493d7887c7d5b0383d72faa993ecba11de9","tid":1605830,"uid":327123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:56:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b6150fa2fb415c450cd1b1db082ab925a47852","tid":1605830,"uid":162866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"850508db1a55ba73bc01938346de12d32a9ffe13","tid":1605830,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":